ʻOku lolotonga lele hoʻo tamasiʻi akó ke ʻosi mei he akó. ʻOku lelei ʻaupito ʻeni. ʻOku ʻuhinga ʻeni te ne ʻosi mei heʻene cohort pea mateuteu ki he meʻa hono hoko.
ʻOku mavahe hoʻo tamasiʻi akó mei he ʻosi mei he akó. Tokoniʻi hoʻo tokotaha ako ke foki ki he hala. Fokotuʻutuʻu ha fakataha mo e ʻetivaisa hoʻo fānau akó ke fai ha palani ngāue.
ʻOku ʻikai ha fakamatala ke lava ʻo fakaʻuhingaʻi.
